race.comment: Competitive contest. BENFICA LASS (13) has been thereabouts in all five starts this campaign and is more than capable enough on her day. Will be rock hard fit for this and a strong showing would not surprise. PELE PRINCESS (14) is drawn to get all the favours from the inside alley and is a two-time winner here. Looks a must for the exotics players. AUNTY RENE (6) gets 2kg off with the claim and will be ready to peak now. Top-three credentials. FLYING BAT (4) goes well for Vitler who has two wins from just three steers. Right in the mix. AUTUMNGIRL (12) rounds out the selections in a race decimated by key scratchings.
